OL,3,CFormer Camelot boss named as new
OL,4,Cchairman of troubled Post Office
OL,6,FThe former boss of Camelot, which used
OL,7,Fto operate the National Lottery, has
OL,8,Fbeen named as the new interim chairman
OL,9,Fof the scandal-hit Post Office.
OL,11,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch
OL,12,Fappointed Nigel Railton to the post,
OL,13,Freplacing Henry Staunton ` who was
OL,14,Fsacked in January.
OL,16,FThe government said Mr Railton will
OL,17,Ftake up the role at the state-owned
OL,18,FPost Office "as soon as possible",
OL,19,Ffollowing pre-appointment checks.
