OL,3,CFormer Camelot boss named as new
OL,4,Cchairman of troubled Post Office
OL,6,FIt said he has the necessary
OL,7,Fexperience of "transforming
OL,8,Forganisations" to take on the role.
OL,10,FThe former chief executive of Camelot,
OL,11,Fwhich handed over the running of the
OL,12,FNational Lottery to Allwyn in February
OL,13,Fafter losing the licence, will take on
OL,14,Fthe job as the Post Office looks to
OL,15,Fpay long-delayed compensation to
OL,16,Fvictims of the Horizon IT scandal.
