OL,3,CFormer Camelot boss named as new
OL,4,Cchairman of troubled Post Office
OL,6,FIt comes as the Post Office is subject
OL,7,Fto an ongoing public inquiry into the
OL,8,Faffair, which saw hundreds of innocent
OL,9,Fsubpostmasters wrongly convicted as a
OL,10,Fresult of faulty Horizon software.
OL,12,FMr Saunton's sacking led to which saw
OL,13,Fboth sides accuse the other of
OL,14,Fmishandling the Horizon scandal.
OL,16,FMr Staunton claimed he had been told
OL,17,Fto delay payouts to the sub-
OL,18,Fpostmasters by the government,
OL,19,Fsomething Ms Badenoch strenuously
OL,20,Fdenied.
