OL,3,CFormer Camelot boss named as new
OL,4,Cchairman of troubled Post Office
OL,6,FAfter appointing Mr Railton, Ms
OL,7,FBadenoch said: "Nigel has the
OL,8,Fnecessary experience to lead an
OL,9,Forganisation as large and complex as
OL,10,Fthe Post Office and I'm confident he
OL,11,Fwill work well with the leadership
OL,12,Fteam to implement the change that is
OL,13,Frequired in the organisation.
OL,15,F"The government is committed to
OL,16,Fdelivering justice for the
OL,17,Fpostmasters, but also fulfil our
OL,18,Fduties to Post Office staff.
