OL,3,CFormer Camelot boss named as new
OL,4,Cchairman of troubled Post Office
OL,6,F"I want to thank Nigel for stepping up
OL,7,Fto public service at a time of need,
OL,8,Fand I know he can help fix the issues
OL,9,Fof the past whilst transforming the
OL,10,Fcompany for the future."
OL,12,FMr Railton said: "This is an
OL,13,Fincredibly challenging time for the
OL,14,FPost Office as it works to address
OL,15,Fhistoric failures while also striving
OL,16,Fto transform its business."
