OL,7,Fyears until he stepped down in
OL,8,FFebruary 2023 amid a shake-up as it
OL,9,Fwas bought by Allwyn ahead of the
OL,10,Flottery licence handover.
OL,12,FHe also chairs London-listed currency
OL,13,Fmanagement services firm Argentex
OL,14,FGroup.
